Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.59,0:00:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,An murder-swap game that was played without me realising it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.10,0:00:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- My loved one was taken away...\N- Nana-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.10,0:00:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after I decided to revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to profile the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All disturbing events happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people die in that apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of a murder-swap game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't keep up with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.60,0:00:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Did you see Soichi?\N- No...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The child is missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Soichi is not an ordinary child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ~ We are the children of science
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.61,0:00:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ~ It's time for everyone today ~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What…!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.40,0:00:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone may be killed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I was doing an experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.48,0:01:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just say!?\NHey! Hey…!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.87,0:01:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Good….
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective, this boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take him!\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anyone who was close to Sawa Kuroshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.49,0:01:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... yes.\NYes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, the last time you met Ms. Kuroshima...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That... yes, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Ms. Kuroshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, she was able to avoid collision with the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She was hit hard on the head by the impact of the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The situation is unpredictable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but it's an ongoing investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We checked the security camera,\Nbut there are several people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't know who pushed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- That video...\N- Can you show me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.94,0:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As is expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:03:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a friend?\NDo you have any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.38,0:03:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was suddenly called by Professor Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Hayakawa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Kuroshima wrote Hayakawa name in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I see….
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.95,0:03:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, the Student Affairs Office of the University is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, We're going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is bad timing.\N- Timing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a rumor that you might be in a disciplinary meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.93,0:03:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Masashi Enomoto
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,started talking about your past bribery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, incidents around the condo are continuing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you didn't report about the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your conviction is terrible and you could be dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Well, it might be better for you to deliver rignment letter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.99,0:04:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,before your career is damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Think carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.92,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't have time to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I make my decision quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.45,0:04:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...\NThe detectives were calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here, so you'd better go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Doyan, Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... totally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But you already got me one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?\NYou must be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only worry now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm worried as much as I can.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I worry, sometimes people worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible because I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- So my wife...\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- She is out of danger.\N- Ah... is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And Soichi, was imprisoned in a juvenile classification home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The charge is as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempted murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But he is still my beloved son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.89,0:06:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tell you,\NAs for Soichi's interrogation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Each animal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,has a different way of opening its pupils when it dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And what would that be like for a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I heard that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How should I look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't blame myself for him turning out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You said he used to be handcuffed only when going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Soichi's statement,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.37,0:06:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,he went out of the room
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and broke into Fujii's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.48,0:06:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ~ We are the children of science
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ ~ 1234
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there a threat video?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamagiwa was my classmate at university.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I hated him since the old days
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you send them together,\NIt will be effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi Fujii.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...\NTechnology nowadays is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to do eveything to help my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can say now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Doyan Doyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.42,0:08:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go home.\N- No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Her parents are here, and we will bother them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- I'm pretty sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The third person in the room that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.57,0:08:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I make decision quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I make decision quickly
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- That detective.\N- Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\Ndo you mean the partner of the Enomoto couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah first\Nthere were three people in that room...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.55,0:08:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nana-chan\N- Shota...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, there was only that couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.93,0:08:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When Kuroshima was discovered in room 303...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that no one was around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he betray and run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If Enomoto and his wife are not talking to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a possibility that they are still in cahoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better not to rush and ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure he's cornered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as Masashi Enomoto stated
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you leak the date of the illegal casino raid and receive money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As a condition of silence
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You deliberately neglected to report\Non the murder-swap game
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to cause confusion about the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get caught
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell all about what you did two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I'll take responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- Resignment...\N- Don't jump to conclusions, Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.92,0:09:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,However, as Mr. Enomoto says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.42,0:09:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will admit an assault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Assault?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We only heard about the bribery from Enomoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NWere you doing anything else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey Kamiya!\N- Ah….
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the bribery story
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a fight with Enomoto in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.98,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What were you doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I was witnessed by the resident
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. You're idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe disciplinary dismissal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- You asked for it.\N- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the inconvenience!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be contempt for me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.38,0:10:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I donn't hate Mr. Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hate?\NIt's subtlely rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! If you're sorry,\NI'll do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Whatever you do now...\N- No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the case where many people were killed.\NIf you can solve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is chance that you will be able to\Nreceive only suspension as punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But from now, I'm under suspension.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So! I solved it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it all your credit...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Expect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.45,0:11:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So Sora was discharged\Nfrom the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried about his physical condition,\Nbut I'm still worried about his mental state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- The analysis of Soichi was right.\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, what AI did during this period was
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.97,0:11:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,just looking for people who were\Nmore likely to commit pleasure killings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Soichi had an alibi when Nana was killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the database of past crimes has increased.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look at the analysis result based on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the killings of Nana,\NAkaike couple, and Mr. Ukita
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The possibility of the same culprit is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you try to narrow down the criteria for each item.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The reliability will decreased.\NBut in case of same culprit
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you add Kayo Kojima to the victim's data
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The reliability does not change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- In other words...\N- The culprit who killed Nana-san
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,is very likely to kill these five peaple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the purpose….
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As a result, the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Still uncertain.\NDon't run out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mr. Nishimura, this.\N- Yes, I will take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.38,0:13:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,1400 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a private receipt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's magic when I drew a poster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then please bring that magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What we bought with the budget of the residents' association\NIt belongs to the residents' association.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Do you have receipt?\N- Mr. Nishimura...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Me?\N- Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- I need to talk to Mr. Tezuka.\N- Can I do it later?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Not good.\N- Hey! Are you going to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, I'm going to get that magic...\N- This person is really strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When the manager died
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.46,0:13:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where were you?\N- Do not ignore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching TV in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just in front of the manager room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a small sound that the metal rubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.41,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I had the opportunity to\Nhear the same sound later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What were\Nyou doing in the manager room at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... There was something I lent to the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to remind him but he was out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you lend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A mahjong mat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while, it was returned as new.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Nishimura here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes\N- Please accept this as a token of apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you mean by apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.93,0:14:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that he made a hole\Nwith a cigarette...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he bought a new one.\NWasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Mr. Nishimura
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did you know about\Nthe murder-swap game?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Are you still talking about this?\N- This is the last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we go to the restaurant together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you played a dangerous game\Nat the residents' meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a promise to not talk about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told by Ms. Kinoshita later,\Nso I asked at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I explained... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, we aren't told anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey?\N- Huh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will tell you if you\Nreturn my work materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.00,0:15:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if you have a receipt,\Nyou can brought it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.93,0:15:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh yes yes.\N- Oh, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- I missed my budget...\N- I'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can you take it off for a minute?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing I want you to answer honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have heard about Soichi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.91,0:16:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Until this time,\Neven Soichi is not doing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- There is a possibility of guilty...\N- I will answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the Akaike couple's incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no plate on the cake left on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't she eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I ate...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Be honest.\N- Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, Nana-san was watching the cake
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.39,0:17:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I also noticed it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.44,0:17:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Culprit was trying to make the case
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.51,0:17:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the game-related murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,While everyone was taking care of Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I contacted the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, if the police noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a possibility\Nthat your sin would be found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.95,0:17:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After all whose name did you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Mr. Tokoshima...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the property manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes….
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kamiya, This is bad!\NI heard you're under suspension?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mizuki, There is new\Ninformation from Sanae Enomoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm helping you because I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.41,0:18:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me summarize the numbers.\NIt is a little red.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- I want to make up for it from the reserve.\N- Yeah, more important than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One of you did it again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,On the railway!\NWhat does this mean!? It's scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about anything you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.03,0:18:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, please tell the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Don't distract me. Are you a killer?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.42,0:18:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we looking for Sora together?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's right.\N- Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tezuka, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because “I will kill all the residents of this condominium.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Haa!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a massacre?\NWill you keep killing until the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- I said that.\N- Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you only said that to Ms. Ono?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.93,0:19:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so enthusiastic about the incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.99,0:19:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's right!\N- Isn't too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- just for curiosity?\N- That's all for the checkout...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, sorry it's for the work.\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ha?\N- As I thought you're a reporter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you guys didn't know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't know.\N- Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't know...\N- I'm still not famous enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.01,0:19:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.41,0:19:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,“Entertainer who tried to live in\Na place that incident happened”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is The Southern Cross Minami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,One week has passed since I lived\Nin a property a 15-minute walk from Sakai Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,From the first day, it gradually thickened.\NHere is an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the grudge of the person who died in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you shoot this kind of video in this apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I don't feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't sell until this year.\NI'm not talented at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,In this kind of niche\NI have to do something extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\NYou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It hurts... Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you keep going.\NIt can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make fun of it, so help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.91,0:20:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey...!\N- Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Calm down!\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you say the same thing if Kuroshima died!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If It can be solved by violent, I'll do…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't solve this without the cooperation\Nof the residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There is something I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.95,0:21:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's finished.\N- What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.92,0:21:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I installed the app I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for Tezuka who\Ntends to take extreme actions
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.54,0:21:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of it as an amulet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Amulet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.43,0:21:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally developed for elderly people\Nwho lost their spouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh... what?\N- So
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This app allows you to talk with Nana.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, For now,\NIt can speak only simple things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.49,0:22:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,By talking back and forth,\NIt will become closer to the person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.91,0:22:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Doyan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When anger cannot be suppressed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,When you became hopelessly lonely.\NTalk to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... If you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Shota-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Shota-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.41,0:23:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.93,0:23:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Come home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.96,0:23:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.01,0:23:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.90,0:23:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.42,0:23:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.89,0:23:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'd protect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See to it that the culprit is lured and act on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was stopped by Nana-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That was exactly what Nana says.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.40,0:24:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I can't solve...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.90,0:24:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,with just love.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.44,0:24:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.49,0:24:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.40,0:24:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.92,0:24:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.40,0:24:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.92,0:24:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.48,0:24:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.00,0:25:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the reasons for Kamiya's suspension.\NHe will probably be dismissed
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.94,0:25:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys don't act like idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.43,0:25:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.95,0:25:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- Then Mizuki! Progress report.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.40,0:25:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With the assumption that the game was played.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.40,0:25:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've confirmed the alibi of the residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.92,0:25:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no change.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.97,0:25:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawa Kuroshima, who is hospitalized,\Nhas an alibi in every incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.91,0:25:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true that Sanae Enomoto wrote\Nthe name of Hiroshi Tokoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.40,0:25:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, however at the estimated time of death of Tokoshima
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.90,0:25:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The couple had an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.42,0:25:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it possible that his son Soichi Enomoto killed Tokoshima?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.92,0:25:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't know\N- But...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.46,0:25:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He is now proudly testifying about his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.40,0:25:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If he killed Tokoshima, I think he would confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.41,0:26:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If it was a game, the person who drew the paper might have killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.44,0:26:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm calling many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.44,0:26:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kamiya\NPlease call me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.40,0:26:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.38,0:26:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Nikaido,\NI'm sorry you had to come every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.42,0:26:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.90,0:26:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so kind coming every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.89,0:26:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your kind offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.44,0:26:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh yes!\N- I'll keep an eye on Sawacho properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.38,0:26:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly... I can't believe she have friends in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.92,0:26:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will contact you if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.41,0:26:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.43,0:27:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here, so Ms. Ono...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.50,0:27:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to be alone with Nikaido.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.89,0:27:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Two people alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.89,0:27:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Would you like to eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.95,0:27:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I made these wafers myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.95,0:27:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.94,0:27:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't eat what people made.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.98,0:27:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll eat it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.91,0:28:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you often have such medical accidents?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.94,0:28:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes... but it is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.50,0:28:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Potassium chloride takes about 2 hours to drop the drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.95,0:28:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it for a short time, it will cause heart failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.92,0:28:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.44,0:28:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please ask me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.96,0:28:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I usually only talk to my coworkers or patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.46,0:28:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fun to talk to a healthy amateur person.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.45,0:28:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.42,0:28:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anyone, but please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.41,0:28:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived 10 years in blood and sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.43,0:28:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My face must have changed
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.97,0:28:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, it's nice!\N- No! Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.00,0:28:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Is it okay? Your role is
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.44,0:28:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,A benefactor who helped this child 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.44,0:28:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're ashamed of yourself with\Nthe past that killed people.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.41,0:29:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If she found out that a benefactor whom she has been searching for 10 years
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.41,0:29:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Was a gangster,\Nshe'll be shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.43,0:29:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I leave without revealing my circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.95,0:29:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!\NThat's totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.99,0:29:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then if Mr. Tamiya does it...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.42,0:29:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've lived 10 years in blood and sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.43,0:29:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My face must have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.43,0:29:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have clear eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.90,0:29:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.42,0:29:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's human slaughter! Drifter...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.47,0:29:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying my eyes are clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.45,0:29:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What a funny girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.45,0:29:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thanks for your work ~\N- Thanks for your work
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.53,0:29:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bother you ~
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.45,0:29:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you already know,\NKono was my subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.44,0:30:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You met him at the bank just before he died, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.43,0:30:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I warned him about the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.46,0:30:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you doubt me?\NIf I was going to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.02,0:30:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't meet him at the old office.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.92,0:30:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But there were troubles at the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.02,0:30:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah… Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.02,0:30:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Innocence!! I'm clear!!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.43,0:30:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.00,0:30:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because there were many people who had the same shallow doubts as you
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.41,0:30:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.62,0:30:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you were the person who put the surveillance camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.17,0:30:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To solve the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.06,0:30:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't help though.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.58,0:30:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way... Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.08,0:30:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mizuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.07,0:30:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes….
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.12,0:30:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's about Mr. Takafumi Kono...\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.66,0:30:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It took a long time to analyze\Nthe video of the security camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.10,0:31:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There were several people who are especially suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.10,0:31:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,They were all about 170 cm tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.07,0:31:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 178.54.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.09,0:31:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're surprisingly tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.11,0:31:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.\NThank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.10,0:31:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Excuse me….
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.11,0:31:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, only the legs have been discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.70,0:31:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to ask you something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.60,0:31:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Some fingerprints of strangers were found in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.59,0:32:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The police found some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.63,0:32:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But at that time, there was a trouble at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.63,0:32:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That….
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.65,0:32:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You also lost your wife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.19,0:32:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.59,0:32:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you love your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.61,0:32:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.61,0:32:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you let your wife know how much you love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.12,0:32:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.64,0:32:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.69,0:32:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.10,0:32:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.57,0:32:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But we didn't look in different directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.57,0:32:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a little distance, but we went in the same direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.06,0:32:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We were running side by side.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.63,0:32:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's always someone somewhere in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.07,0:33:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an excuse.\NI was cheating on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.60,0:33:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.\N“AI Nana-chan”.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.66,0:33:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a machine, but it was not just a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.57,0:33:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You should express your feelings properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.56,0:33:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.58,0:33:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Doyan may be not good at express your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.58,0:33:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still love that overflows.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.12,0:33:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.56,0:33:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Doyan feel like your love is acting on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.06,0:34:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stop yourself from trying to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.07,0:34:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.57,0:34:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's when
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.55,0:34:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroshima woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.11,0:35:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But... Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.61,0:35:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, you've called me many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.18,0:35:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.20,0:35:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.12,0:35:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.10,0:35:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.05,0:36:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.59,0:36:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.64,0:36:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.08,0:36:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's okay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.07,0:36:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to get in touch when you go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.07,0:36:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.07,0:36:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fu ~.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.08,0:36:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Angelina ~!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.60,0:36:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Angelina!\NAngelina...!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.64,0:37:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Angelina! I'm back…!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.69,0:37:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.60,0:37:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you,\NMy name is Yoshihiko Hakamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.59,0:37:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard it helps to get back memory
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.61,0:37:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you live in the same environment as before,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.60,0:37:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you familiar with that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.13,0:37:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.15,0:37:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And here is Kuzumi's room?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.59,0:37:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.61,0:37:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Hakamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.59,0:37:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.10,0:37:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.10,0:37:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.07,0:37:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it pretending to be memory loss?\NMr. Kuzumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.09,0:37:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- Um... I'm Hakamada.\N- No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.64,0:37:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You just said,\N“I'm back” or “Long time no see”.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.59,0:37:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I was listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.58,0:37:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha I don't understand,\NCould you go through the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.60,0:38:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuzumi is lying!\NKuzumi is a murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.60,0:38:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Fujii!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.60,0:38:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.11,0:38:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.14,0:38:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you notice it so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.58,0:38:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NActually, I did it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.60,0:38:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- I guess so.\N- Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.60,0:38:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to speak honestly and cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.61,0:38:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I even beat the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.58,0:38:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, how could you?\N- It's that….
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.66,0:38:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Doyan doesn't get irritated because you like Kuroshima-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.16,0:38:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great to meet such people
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.60,0:39:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nikaido...?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.08,0:39:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma This is Chiunque Kuramae.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.14,0:39:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The apartment where the grandma lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.61,0:39:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.10,0:39:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce people who live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.58,0:39:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,101 is Kuzumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.60,0:40:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,102 is Kayo Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.11,0:40:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She had an English class in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.18,0:40:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 103 is...\N- As always, You're not good at talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.07,0:40:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.08,0:40:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\NAnd I don't know what to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.09,0:40:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.57,0:40:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, would you like something to drink?\N- I will drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.59,0:40:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.60,0:40:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need to ask again?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.13,0:40:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ask, would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.69,0:40:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how to use particles.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.07,0:40:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh and then I want to have tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.09,0:40:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I will buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.59,0:40:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.08,0:40:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I will pay by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.10,0:40:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You asked me to borrow you.\NYou can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.66,0:40:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.63,0:40:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.58,0:41:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.10,0:41:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was really relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.10,0:41:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.59,0:41:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's take a photo together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.12,0:41:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Before
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.66,0:41:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Doyan feel like your love is acting on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.61,0:41:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See, Sawa, laugh, laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.08,0:41:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.12,0:41:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Nikaido, would you like to take a picture together?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.12,0:41:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.16,0:41:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't talk about anything, just being there is fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.63,0:41:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.10,0:41:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah….
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.61,0:42:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What I wrote on paper was
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.10,0:42:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kayo Kojima
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.60,0:42:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.60,0:42:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah ~!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.10,0:43:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Ah ah ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.60,0:43:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Orangutan time.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.63,0:43:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Orangutan time!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.10,0:43:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma was not participating in the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.09,0:43:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a high possibility that\Nthis paper was drawn by Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.64,0:43:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mrs. Kojima was killed\Nafter Misato died.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.60,0:43:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,\NMisato did not kill Mrs. Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.60,0:43:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ukita.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.12,0:43:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.11,0:43:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Akaike couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.63,0:43:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a murderer who killed\Nthese five people, including Mrs. Kojima.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.60,0:43:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Nana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.64,0:43:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's bullseye.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.59,0:44:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?\NDon't tell you're going to cancel.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.60,0:44:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, can we meet earlier than planned?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.60,0:44:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I know who killed your wife.
